			printf("THANK YOU FOR USING OUR BANKING SYSTEM. PLEASE VISIT AGAIN. HAVE A NICE DAY!\n");
			printf("-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------	\n");
			printf("PLEASE RE-LOGIN TO COMMIT ANOTHER SERVICE\n");
